{"tid":821154,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有時我覺得自己係一條三文魚","createTime":"2018-09-15T21:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T02:57:05.000Z","uid":11598,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0600382ab9dff4e0c165ce76147514e6260a9d4","tid":821154,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:28:40.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得自己係一條三文魚<br />\n細細個就已經要係個海度浮浮沉沉唔知為乜<br />\n讀書一向唔係我嘅興趣 自然讀到一pat屎咁<br />\n好啦 大個咗覺得係時候要揾人生意義 但係連自己到底想點都未知<br />\n咩叫目標 點解人哋可以咁有動力去搵自己嘅目標<br />\n最後就變咗刺身咁任人魚肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攰了 瞓覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2caf35e574c0e27d7e89693b4a0ab7275a2cb8f","tid":821154,"uid":88025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:30:27.000Z","msg":"加油！我信你會揾到嫁！"},{"pid":"9af6da621ff26ddb2649f0de4525231b96e92281","tid":821154,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:31:54.000Z","msg":"刺身都叫點下wasabi俾人食得下 但係你咩都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612e38a17c279d18513f2e9bba65f4824b57980b","tid":821154,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:32:45.000Z","msg":"加油！我信你會揾到嫁！"},{"pid":"0f70c333ca2cb6136b2e35922c4776cd1ec0e8cc","tid":821154,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"612e38a17c279d18513f2e9bba65f4824b57980b","tid":821154,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:32:45.000Z","msg":"加油！我信你會揾到嫁！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:35:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老濛"},{"pid":"2f8a6303ff451619c534f2b2ec593a42014e36db","tid":821154,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f70c333ca2cb6136b2e35922c4776cd1ec0e8cc","tid":821154,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"612e38a17c279d18513f2e9bba65f4824b57980b","tid":821154,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-